            <block class="mm_readingText">
                <h2>BE CAREFUL! TURTLES CROSSING!</h2>
                <p>Some animals use the sun, moon, and stars as clues to find which way to go. Baby turtles don’t have <sSpan class="mm_inlineNumber mm_halfSpace">1</sSpan><dropDown id="dropDown_1" example="y">
                        <item id="item_1" correct="y">maps</item>
                        <item id="item_2">watches</item>
                    </dropDown> to get to the <sSpan class="mm_inlineNumber mm_halfSpace">2</sSpan><dropDown id="dropDown_2">
                        <item id="item_1">town</item>
                        <item id="item_2" correct="y">ocean</item>
                    </dropDown>! They use the light from the moon. And they need to get to the water as quickly as they can. Lights from houses and cars can <sSpan class="mm_inlineNumber mm_halfSpace">3</sSpan><dropDown id="dropDown_3">
                        <item id="item_1">help</item>
                        <item id="item_2" correct="y">confuse</item>
                    </dropDown> them. They go the wrong way and sometimes try to cross roads, which is very dangerous. But <sSpan class="mm_inlineNumber mm_halfSpace">4</sSpan><dropDown id="dropDown_4">
                        <item id="item_1" correct="y">everyone</item>
                        <item id="item_2">no one</item>
                    </dropDown> can help. When there are baby turtles, please turn <sSpan class="mm_inlineNumber mm_halfSpace">5</sSpan><dropDown id="dropDown_5">
                        <item id="item_1">on</item>
                        <item id="item_2" correct="y">off</item>
                    </dropDown> your lights! Don’t use <sSpan class="mm_inlineNumber mm_halfSpace">6</sSpan><dropDown id="dropDown_6">
                        <item id="item_1" correct="y">flashlights</item>
                        <item id="item_2">computers</item>
                    </dropDown> or <sSpan class="mm_inlineNumber mm_halfSpace">7</sSpan><dropDown id="dropDown_7">
                        <item id="item_1" correct="y">light fires</item>
                        <item id="item_2">play music</item>
                    </dropDown> on the beach at night. Then the turtles will get to the water safely.</p>
            </block>
        </block>
